---
// Availability Hold receipt page shown after a successful checkout return.
// Receives ?session_id= from Stripe success_url
// Option A strict gate: checkout is available only after server-side availability confirmation.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Availability Hold Received — Happy Faces LA</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 540px; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 1.25rem; box-shadow: 0 1px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 2.5rem; }
    .icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.65; color: #475569; margin: 0.75rem 0; }
    .notice { background: #fff7ed; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
    .notice strong { color: #c2410c; }
    ul { padding-left: 1.25rem; color: #475569; }
    li { margin: 0.5rem 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1.75rem; }
    .btn-primary { background: #f97316; color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #fff; color: #475569; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">🎉</div>
      <h1>Availability Hold received</h1>
      <p>
        Thank you. Your Availability Hold was received by Happy Faces LA.
        We will review your event details and follow up with the next steps.
      </p>

      <div class="notice">
        <strong>Not final yet.</strong><br />
        Your booking is not final until Happy Faces LA confirms artist availability
        and sends confirmation.
      </div>

      <p><strong>What happens next:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>We review your event details and artist availability.</li>
        <li>You receive the next-step email from Happy Faces LA.</li>
        <li>The remaining balance is due closer to your event date.</li>
        <li>A Happy Faces LA artist shows up ready to make every child smile!</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 1.25rem;">
        Questions? Email us or call — your booking reference is in your Stripe receipt email.
        If you don't see it, check your spam folder.
      </p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
        <a href="/plan-my-party/" class="btn-secondary">Plan Another Party</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
